---
title: Seared Scallops and Broccolini with Thai Red Curry Cream Sauce
description: Seared scallops are quick to cook and so tasty! Tonight, they're paired with a rich red curry sauce, ginger-garlic broccolini and fragrant lemongrass rice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/petoncles-saisis-et-broccolini-5d14026f.jpg
